tiles.title: PRIV01 TX Drops
tiles.query:
interface 
| where precise_timestamp  between (_startTime .. _endTime)
| where t0_interface has "PRIV01" 
| where t0_interface contains _tnt
| project precise_timestamp,  t0_interface, rx_dropped_packets 
| order by t0_interface, precise_timestamp
| extend rx_dropped_packets_delta = rx_dropped_packets- next(rx_dropped_packets), rx_dropped_packets_next = next(rx_dropped_packets) 
| project  precise_timestamp, t0_interface, rx_dropped_packets_delta

tiles.title: PRIV01 RX Packets Per Second
tiles.query:
interface 
| where precise_timestamp  between (_startTime .. _endTime)
| where t0_interface has "PRIV01" 
| where t0_interface contains _tnt
| project precise_timestamp,  t0_interface, rx_total_packets,last_update_timestamp 
| order by t0_interface, precise_timestamp
| extend rx_total_packets_delta = rx_total_packets- next(rx_total_packets)
| extend total_time = (todouble(last_update_timestamp) - todouble(next(last_update_timestamp)))/1000
| extend  rx_packets_per_second = rx_total_packets_delta / total_time
